Package com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms

Class Mission

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms.Mission
  • @Entity
public class Mission
extends java.lang.Object
    The Mission class represents a mission in the database. It contains information about the ID, cluster, source, reward, shareability, kills required, progress, expiry, accept time, completion status, and kills left of the mission. It also contains methods to get and set these attributes.
